x_n = n(\sqrt{n^2+1} - n)\sin\dfrac{n\pi}8
n\in\Bbb{N}
\limsup x_n
x_n = \sup C(x_n)
x_n
n · \left( \sqrt{n²+1} - n \right) = n · \tfrac{1}{\sqrt{n²+1} + n}
n ∈ ℕ
\tfrac{\sqrt{n²+1} + n}{n} = \sqrt{1+\tfrac{1}{n²}} + 1 \overset{n → ∞}{\longrightarrow} 2
n · \left( \sqrt{n²+1} - n \right) \overset{n → ∞}{\longrightarrow} \tfrac{1}{2}
x_n = n · \left( \sqrt{n²+1} - n \right) · \sin \left(\tfrac{n · π}{8}\right) ≤ n · \left( \sqrt{n²+1} - n \right)
n ∈ ℕ
\sin \left(\tfrac{(16n+4)· π}{8}\right) = \sin \left(n·2π + \tfrac{π}{2}\right) = \sin \left(\tfrac{π}{2}\right)= 1
n ∈ ℕ
x_{16n+4} = (16n+4) · \left( \sqrt{(16n+4)²+1} - (16n+4) \right) · \sin \left(\tfrac{(16n+4)· π}{8}\right) \overset{n → ∞}{\longrightarrow} \tfrac{1}{2}
\tfrac{1}{2}
(x_n)_{n ∈ ℕ}
